ually the period of suspension</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h3>Qualifying rules</h3>\n\n<p>To qualify, you must: </p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>have been in paid work </li>\n  <li>have worked the right number of hours before you go on leave or the gap happens</li>\n  <li>get Statutory Sick Pay or an equivalent benefit (sick leave only) </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The equivalent benefits are <a href=\"/boost-state-pension\" title=\"National Insurance Credits\">National Insurance Credit</a> (incapacity for work element), Employment and Support Allowance or Income Support (incapacity for work element).</p>\n\n<h2>What you need to do</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"/changes-affect-tax-credits\" title=\"Changes that affect your tax credits\">Report any changes</a> to your work or family life to the Tax Credit Office to make sure you get paid the right amount of tax credit. </p>\n"}]},"tags":[{"title":"Tax credits","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/benefits%2Ftax-credits.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes Working Tax Credit, Child Tax Credit and when tax credits stop","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=benefits%2Ftax-credits","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/benefits/tax-credits"},"parent":{"title":"Benefits","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/benefits.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes tax credits and eligibility","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=benefits","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/benefits"},"parent":null}}],"related":[{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/qualify-tax-credits-quick-questionnaire.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/qualify-tax-credits-quick-questionnaire","title":"Do you qualify for tax credits - quick questionnaire","format":"answer","updated_at":"2012-10-22T15:13:37+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tax-credits-calculator.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/tax-credits-